# --- Claude Code dev container ---

# Personal working copies (bind-mounted / baked into the container). Each dev
# keeps their own; the committed *.example files are the shared baseline.
/CLAUDE.md
/claude.json

# Kept TRACKED (no secrets in either):
#   CLAUDE.md.example    -> agent-memory baseline; copy to CLAUDE.md on first setup
#   claude.json.example  -> MCP config-as-code; PAT injected at runtime, rest use OAuth
# (Noted here only as a reminder; they are intentionally NOT ignored.)

# Environment file: holds GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN, PROJECTS_DIR, etc.
/.env

# Machine-specific compose override (per-project node_modules volumes, etc.).
# Commit docker-compose.override.yml.example instead.
/docker-compose.override.yml